# capacitor / iOS build artifacts
# `ios/App/Pods/` and `ios/App/App/public/` are generated by
# `npx cap add ios` + `npx cap sync ios` and should be rebuilt
# on every CI / dev machine rather than committed. `output/` is
# Xcode's build output dir. The rest of `ios/` IS committed —
# it contains the Xcode project config and Swift sources.
ios/App/Pods/
ios/App/App/public/
ios/App/output/
